abstract: The Day: Chris Christie, who says now is not his time, is a Republican from the Northeast. That fact in itself is a problem. Also, what City Room is reading in other papers and blogs.
snippet: The Day: Chris Christie, who says now is not his time, is a Republican from the Northeast. That fact in itself is a problem. Also, what City Room is reading in other papers and blogs.
lead_paragraph: When former Gov. George E. Pataki announced in August, to the consternation of almost no one, that he would not run for president, I wrote about the backwater that New York had become in national politics.
